PN,46305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1780243866
OL,3,COne in five adults in Wales living
OL,4,Cwith diabetes or prediabetes
OL,6,F"By using our simple Know Your Risk
OL,7,Fonline tool, you can get advice on
OL,8,Fwhether you're at risk and receive
OL,9,Fguidance on what steps to take next.
OL,10,FIt's free and only takes a few
OL,11,Fminutes."
OL,13,FWhat is the difference between type 1
OL,14,Fand type 2 diabetes?
OL,16,FType 1 diabetes is a lifelong
OL,17,Fcondition where the body's immune
OL,18,Fsystem attacks the cells that produce
OL,19,Finsulin, which controls blood glucose.
OL,26,@sD@IO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
