PN,46306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1780243866
OL,3,COne in five adults in Wales living
OL,4,Cwith diabetes or prediabetes
OL,6,FPatients with type 1 diabetes need to
OL,7,Ftake insulin supplements every day to
OL,8,Fkeep blood glucose levels in check.
OL,10,FType 1 diabetes is not linked with age
OL,11,For being overweight, which are factors
OL,12,Flinked to type 2 diabetes.
OL,14,FType 2 diabetes is the most common
OL,15,Ftype, affecting around 90% of people
OL,16,Fwith diabetes in Britain.
OL,18,FThe condition means someone's body
OL,19,Fdoes not produce insulin or does not
OL,20,Freact to insulin properly.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
