PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1780243866
OL,3,COne in five adults in Wales living
OL,4,Cwith diabetes or prediabetes
OL,6,FDr Sarah Davies, GP in Cardiff and
OL,7,FPrimary Care Lead for Diabetes in
OL,8,FWales, said, "We are seeing rising
OL,9,Fnumbers of people being diagnosed with
OL,10,Ftype 2 diabetes in Wales, with
OL,11,Fespecially fast-growing numbers in
OL,12,Fpeople under the age of 40.
OL,14,F"We see type 2 diabetes more commonly
OL,15,Fin people with strong family histories
OL,16,Fof type 2 diabetes, in people who live
OL,17,Fwith overweight, obesity or other
OL,18,Fconditions such as high blood pressure.
OL,26,@pD@NOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
