OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1780243866
OL,3,COne in five adults in Wales living
OL,4,Cwith diabetes or prediabetes
OL,6,F"If we can support people to
OL,7,Funderstand their risk of developing
OL,8,Ftype 2 diabetes and how they can take
OL,9,Faction to reduce it."
OL,11,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said,
OL,12,F"One of the first actions of this new
OL,13,Fadministration was to create a new
OL,14,FMinister for Public and Preventive
OL,15,FHealth, with a targeted focus on
OL,16,Fsupporting the environment and access
OL,17,Ffor healthier choices to reduce the
OL,18,Frisk of chronic conditions like
OL,19,Fobesity and Type 2 diabetes.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
