OL,3,COne in five adults in Wales living
OL,4,Cwith diabetes or prediabetes
OL,6,F"We recognise the importance of
OL,7,Fprevention to improve public health
OL,8,Fand ensuring that all Government
OL,9,Fpolicy is aligned towards the goal of
OL,10,Fcreating a healthier population."
